    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1906-06-02T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1906-06-02T00:00:00-05:00" n="372"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d372">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to Minister
                            <persName type="to">Barrett</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Extract]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-06-02">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 2, 1906</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Say to President Reyes that I am most favorably impressed by his proposals and
                    shall be glad to undertake negotiation on general lines suggested by him.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Root</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
